From: Eugenia Emantayev <eugenia@mellanox.co.il>
Date: Thu, 19 Jan 2012 09:44:37 +0000
Subject: mlx4: VF is not allowed to perform dump stats
Patch-mainline: v3.3-rc2
Git-commit: 35fb9afbdeef9d5859d9a878d0372907baf119e1
References: bnc#786036 FATE#314304

In multifunction mode - DUMP_STATS command is not executed
for VFs.

Signed-off-by: Eugenia Emantayev <eugenia@mellanox.co.il>
Reviewed-by: Yevgeny Petrilin <yevgenyp@mellanox.co.il>
Signed-off-by: David S. Miller <davem@davemloft.net>
Signed-off-by: Amir Vadai <amirv@mellanox.com>
Acked-by: Benjamin Poirier <bpoirier@suse.de>
---
 drivers/net/ethernet/mellanox/mlx4/port.c |    2 ++
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+)
--- a/drivers/net/ethernet/mellanox/mlx4/port.c
+++ b/drivers/net/ethernet/mellanox/mlx4/port.c
@@ -897,6 +897,8 @@ int mlx4_DUMP_ETH_STATS_wrapper(struct m
 				struct mlx4_cmd_mailbox *outbox,
 				struct mlx4_cmd_info *cmd)
 {
+	if (slave != dev->caps.function)
+		return 0;
 	return mlx4_common_dump_eth_stats(dev, slave,
 					  vhcr->in_modifier, outbox);
 }
